name: True Rivalry
description:
100% Purple and Gold, Tis the Season of the True Rivalry!

Live like a champion, dress like a champion!

Rep for the Lakeshow on their road to their 16th championship!  CAN YOU SAY REPEAT!!!!!!!

All shirts are shipped USPS Priority Mail within the United States.  Shirts are shipped either day of or the following day once ordered.

6.1 oz. Ultra Premium 100% preshrunk cotton. Seamless collar. Double-needle stitched throughout. Taped neck, shoulder-to-shoulder. 

Body Width: S=18", M=20", L=22"
